LetsGiftIt,is,a,service,for,group,gifting,It,allows,eCommerce,and,other,product,and,service,providers,to,offer,group,gifting,as,an,option,to,buy,the,goods,or,services,Users,can,use,LetsGiftIt,to,buy,a,gift,for,someone,socially,with,other,people,The,LetsGiftIt,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,LetsGiftIt,functionality,into,other,websites,and,eCommerce,platforms,The,main,method,of,the,API,is,creating,and,adding,gifts,listing,a,title,and,description,of,the,gift,and,other,details,about,the,gift